---
import { Mail } from '@lucide/astro';

import { siteConfig, socialLinks } from '../lib/site';

const githubMarkPath =
  'M12 .297a12 12 0 0 0-3.794 23.385c.6.113.82-.258.82-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.042-1.416-4.042-1.416a3.18 3.18 0 0 0-1.335-1.755c-1.09-.745.083-.729.083-.729a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 1.84 1.237 2.555 2.555 0 0 0 3.49.997 2.554 2.554 0 0 1 .762-1.6C7.16 17.31 4.36 16.27 4.36 11.67a4.573 4.573 0 0 1 1.218-3.172 4.25 4.25 0 0 1 .116-3.127s.996-.318 3.26 1.214a11.274 11.274 0 0 1 5.932 0c2.264-1.532 3.26-1.214 3.26-1.214a4.25 4.25 0 0 1 .116 3.127 4.573 4.573 0 0 1 1.218 3.172c0 4.61-2.804 5.636-5.475 5.932a2.868 2.868 0 0 1 .814 2.224v3.293c0 .322.216.694.825.576A12.003 12.003 0 0 0 12 .297Z';
---

<section class="grid gap-8 pb-10 pt-6 md:grid-cols-[180px_minmax(0,1fr)] md:items-center">
  <div class="md:col-span-2">
    <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
      <img
        class="h-14 w-14 rounded-full border border-border object-cover"
        src={siteConfig.avatar}
        alt="Yunxiang He avatar"
        width="56"
        height="56"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <p class="section-kicker mb-0">个人站点</p>
    </div>

    <h1 class="mb-4 font-bold tracking-[-0.02em]">Hypoxanthine</h1>
    <div class="mb-4 space-y-1 font-sans text-accent">
      <p class="text-[1.125rem] font-medium leading-[1.6]">{siteConfig.tagline}</p>
      <p class="text-[1rem] font-medium leading-[1.6]">{siteConfig.subtitle}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-[780px] space-y-2 text-[1.03rem] text-muted">
      <p>贺云翔，网名 Hypoxanthine，目前在 ShanghaiTech 的 VSPLab 读研，导师 Xin Lou。</p>
      <p>本科阶段做过 NeRF 与 3D Gaussian Splatting 相关工作，研究生阶段转向 Cryo Computing × AI Acceleration。</p>
      <p>这里把研究与工程记录、随笔与练习，以及持续扩张中的 Hypo-* 项目生态放在同一个长期可追溯的站点里。</p>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 font-sans text-sm">
      {socialLinks.map((link, index) => {
        return (
          <>
            {index > 0 && <span class="text-muted">·</span>}
            <a class="social-link" href={link.href} target={link.href.startsWith('http') ? '_blank' : undefined} rel="noreferrer">
              {
                link.label === 'GitHub' ? (
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
                    <path d={githubMarkPath}></path>
                  </svg>
                ) : (
                  <Mail size={16} stroke-width={1.8} aria-hidden="true" />
                )
              }
              {link.label}
            </a>
          </>
        );
      })}
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
